    <h1>Market Penetration</h1>
    <p class="description">A growth strategy focused on increasing market share for an existing product in an existing market. The <strong>lowest-risk growth quadrant</strong> in the Ansoff Matrix — no new products, no new markets, just more of what's already working.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
